{"tid":1993680,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[五一黃金週] [Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (300) [選民登記]","createTime":"2020-04-29T02:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T06:38:31.000Z","uid":36509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e57f024b32709d6531e21b1d0016ef4948b8b203","tid":1993680,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"選民登記5月2日截止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>● 登記表格： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3eO2sFD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3eO2sFD&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=6e8052ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3eO2sFD</a><br />\n● 登記方法<br />\n將選民登記表格連同住址證明（更改住址亦適用）送交選舉事務處，包括：<br />\n1. 郵寄到九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n2. 或傳真至2891 1180<br />\n3. 或掃描表格後電郵至form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n4. 或掃描表格後上載至選舉事務處電子表格上載平台 <a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=662d32fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk</a><br />\n詳情可瀏覽： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KCjVTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KCjVTA&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=36bd4717\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KCjVTA</a><br />\nvia <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2F4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b35c643d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2F4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY%2F&h=a4a184e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/on5a6xh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fon5a6xh.png&h=363771a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1enXD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1enXD0.jpg&h=5297555a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n撐黃店，你今日幫襯咗未？<br />\n首個黃色經濟圈 x 動物森友會既活動將會於明天公佈活動細節<br />\n為鼓勵大家踴躍支持黃店，我地已經準備左大量獎金獎品俾你!<br />\n一齊黎創造一個屬於香港人既黃金週!!<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#黃色經濟圈<br />\n#黃店感謝祭<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃金週x動物森友會活動詳情</span></strong>可參閱 Telegram Channel<br />\n@HKGWKAC <a href=\"https://t.me/HKGWKAC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKGWKAC&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=e7bee667\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKGWKAC</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">五一黃金週活動詳情</span></strong>可參閱 Telegram Channel<br />\n@HKGoldenWeek <a href=\"https://t.me/HKGoldenWeek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKGoldenWeek&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=a0bb4446\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKGoldenWeek</a>"},{"pid":"92cc96a223fbb649d97be8754976dfaac2cd939e","tid":1993680,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(用依個留言右上角三點可以 「以此內容建立新主題」，用網頁版可以的話copy埋置頂嗰堆，</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">用電話開post置頂內容會爆字數，可以留言叫巴絲幫手post返)</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/528ykNe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F528ykNe.gif&h=442ae26c&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">置頂</span>有實用資訊</strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/528ykNe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F528ykNe.gif&h=442ae26c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xijn341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXijn341.jpg&h=b1337394&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">買game前你可能會想知 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，新增合成元素，你要由零開始<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">還債</span></span></del>建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：去朋友／網友座島度一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">股票</span></span></del><br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係...<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFWQrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFWQrY.png&h=8c46d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">圖片來源 YouTube -&gt; rEB1vlAiVxE</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>代理</strong></span></span>，真係要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得Cloud Save／轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」＆「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好反智</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有近400隻。歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b474bf00\" target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">特別版主機</span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc908be30b01b0a7b2c99d2ca373c1e456a0066b","tid":1993680,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">遊戲初期常見問題Q&amp;A // 實用網站 // <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n&bull;由於<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>較時間玩(TT，時間旅人)</strong></span>增加太多不確定因素，出現任何bug恕各巴絲愛莫能助<br />\n&bull;Post<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">超長交易list</span></strong>時請用<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>五重引用</strong></span>(如下)，以免影響討論<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">[quote][quote][quote][quote][quote]\n內容\n[/quote][/quote][/quote][/quote][/quote]</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">An/iOS 「Nintendo Switch Online」app</span></span><br />\n<em><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">可以scan設計QR code，連機時可以快速打字傾計</span></span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nintendo.znca&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=01c5f22a\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znca</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/nintendo-switch-online/id1234806557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fnintendo-switch-online%2Fid1234806557&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=04c1544a\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/nintendo-switch-online/id1234806557</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">遊戲初期常見問題Q&amp;A</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>希望新手問問題前可以望一望先</em></span></span><br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://pastebin.com/kZjMuNXh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FkZjMuNXh&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=75d20c36\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/kZjMuNXh</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">實用網站</span></span><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">排隊網，計大頭菜價，外島資料，設計pattern，設計主題曲，種花計數機，物品大全</span></span></em><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>股(大頭菜)價計算，留意網頁內指示<br />\n<a href=\"https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmikebryant.github.io%2Fac-nh-turnip-prices%2Findex.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=4a825d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html</a><br />\n可以開房俾巴絲排隊，唔駛搞到成個post都係code<br />\n<a href=\"https://turnip.exchange/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fturnip.exchange%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=3fccc2e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://turnip.exchange/</a><br />\n種花計數機<br />\n<a href=\"https://aeonsake.gitlab.io/acnh-flower-breeder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faeonsake.gitlab.io%2Facnh-flower-breeder%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=ad77b5a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://aeonsake.gitlab.io/acnh-flower-breeder/</a><br />\n物品大全<br />\n<a href=\"https://nookplaza.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnookplaza.net%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=c49b6c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://nookplaza.net/</a><br />\n外島旅行攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwuffs.org%2Facnh%2Fmysterytour.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=cfb89f41\" target=\"_blank\">https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html</a><br />\n設計任意pattern，可生成QR code scan落遊戲度，可以匯入任意圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://acpatterns.com/editor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facpatterns.com%2Feditor&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=f00a1803\" target=\"_blank\">https://acpatterns.com/editor</a><br />\n分割圖片做幾個正方形，搭上面一齊用效果更佳<br />\n<a href=\"https://pinetools.com/split-image\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpinetools.com%2Fsplit-image&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=a054f7e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://pinetools.com/split-image</a><br />\n設計主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://tunes.nooknet.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftunes.nooknet.net%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=fd70e524\" target=\"_blank\">https://tunes.nooknet.net/</a><br />\n設計無人島<br />\n<a href=\"https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplanimalcrossing.com%2Fnh%2Fstart%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=0dad8c7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">實用圖片／攻略</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">真假藝術品</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">，風水攻略，種花攻略，簡易全攻略</span></span></em><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">真假藝術品</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1J-pAxNEnqKlpH7YJuUeKVjxVAvsoujQYjQcmQ8q5VCU/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1J-pAxNEnqKlpH7YJuUeKVjxVAvsoujQYjQcmQ8q5VCU%2Fedit&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=47e4259e\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1J-